-------------------------------
 NEWS for R Package "vegclust"
-------------------------------

__Version history__
_Version 1.7.9
1. New option to 'trajectoryLengths' and 'trajectoryAngles' to calculate distances and angles relative to initial survey

_Version 1.7.8
1. New option to 'trajectoryPCoA' and 'trajectoryPlot' to draw survey labels

_Version 1.7.7
1. Bug correction 'stratifyvegdata'

_Version 1.7.6
1. Adapt to Rcpp changes

_Version 1.7.5
1. Now trajectory angles are measured between the direction of the first segment and the direction of the second segment.
2. Now mean and sd of trajectory angles are calculated using functions of package 'circular'
3. Parameter 'add' added to community trajectory analysis to deactivate constant addition in triplets violating the triangle inequality.
4. Update "centerTrajectories" according to Anderson (2017)
5. Improved CTA vignette

_Version 1.7.4
1. Improvement of parameter checking in function 'stratifyvegdata'
2. Documentation of avoca data set
3. New function 'trajectoryPlot'

_Version 1.7.3
1. New function 'trajectoryConvergence'
2. New function 'trajectoryDirectionality'
3. New function 'centerTrajectories'

_Version 1.7.2

1. New function 'trajectoryAngles'.
2. New function 'trajectoryProjection'.
3. New vignette for trajectory analysis.

_Version 1.7.1

1. Package encoding. Changed package and author description.

_Version 1.7.0

1. NEW feature: Trajectory analysis. Functions 'trajectoryDistances', 'trajectoryLengths' and 'trajectoryPCoA.
2. Added option to 'trajectoryDistances' to allow different symmetrization functions (e.g. min) in addition to 'mean'
